; Acrylic test piece: 4 registration holes + outer perimeter
; Tool: 2mm single flute spiral end mill
; Material: 6mm acrylic clamped from above
; X0 Y0 = plate center (no flip)
; Z0 = top of acrylic

G21       ; metric
G90       ; absolute
G17       ; XY plane for arcs
M3 S20000 ; spindle on
G4 P2     ; spin-up dwell

; Total cut depth: 6.5mm (through 6mm acrylic + 0.5mm into spoiler)
; Reduce ACR_TOTAL to ~5.8 in gen_back_gcode.py if you have NO spoiler
; under the acrylic, to leave a thin web that protects the bed.
;
; Hole orbits (2mm bit, 1mm radius):
;   center 3.3mm hole -> orbit radius 0.65mm
;   tab    6.0mm hole -> orbit radius 2.00mm
;
; Perimeter is offset OUTWARD by 1.0mm so the part lands at design size.
; After perimeter releases, the part is loose — your clamps must NOT be
; over the part itself, but anchored to the surrounding waste.

; ---- CENTER 3.3mm: X0.0 Y0.0, orbit r=0.65mm ----
G0 Z5.0
G0 X0.0 Y0.0
G0 X0.65 Y0.0
G1 Z-1.5000 F250  ; pass 1
G2 I-0.65 J0 F700
G1 Z-3.0000 F250  ; pass 2
G2 I-0.65 J0 F700
G1 Z-4.5000 F250  ; pass 3
G2 I-0.65 J0 F700
G1 Z-6.0000 F250  ; pass 4
G2 I-0.65 J0 F700
G1 Z-6.5 F250  ; final depth
G2 I-0.65 J0 F700
G2 I-0.65 J0 F700  ; spring pass
G0 Z5.0

; ---- TAB CENTER 6.0mm: X0.0 Y50.864, orbit r=2.0mm ----
G0 Z5.0
G0 X0.0 Y50.864
G0 X2.0 Y50.864
G1 Z-1.5000 F250  ; pass 1
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G1 Z-3.0000 F250  ; pass 2
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G1 Z-4.5000 F250  ; pass 3
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G1 Z-6.0000 F250  ; pass 4
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G1 Z-6.5 F250  ; final depth
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700  ; spring pass
G0 Z5.0

; ---- TAB RIGHT 6.0mm: X6.35 Y44.514, orbit r=2.0mm ----
G0 Z5.0
G0 X6.35 Y44.514
G0 X8.35 Y44.514
G1 Z-1.5000 F250  ; pass 1
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G1 Z-3.0000 F250  ; pass 2
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G1 Z-4.5000 F250  ; pass 3
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G1 Z-6.0000 F250  ; pass 4
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G1 Z-6.5 F250  ; final depth
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700  ; spring pass
G0 Z5.0

; ---- TAB LEFT 6.0mm: X-6.35 Y44.514, orbit r=2.0mm ----
G0 Z5.0
G0 X-6.35 Y44.514
G0 X-4.35 Y44.514
G1 Z-1.5000 F250  ; pass 1
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G1 Z-3.0000 F250  ; pass 2
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G1 Z-4.5000 F250  ; pass 3
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G1 Z-6.0000 F250  ; pass 4
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G1 Z-6.5 F250  ; final depth
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700
G2 I-2.0 J0 F700  ; spring pass
G0 Z5.0

; ---- OUTER PERIMETER (releases the part) ----
G0 Z5.0
G0 X-0.0000 Y58.2138

; ---- depth Z-1.5 ----
G1 Z-1.5000 F250
G1 X-0.2886 Y58.2081 F600
